<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-12-09T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-12-09T00:00:00-05:00" n="80" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d80">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">740.0011 Pacific War/1107</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Memorandum of Conversation, by the Secretary of
                                    State</hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-12-09">December 9,
                                        1941</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>The Ambassador of Colombia<note n="38" xml:id="d80fn1">Gabriel
                                    Turbay.</note> called at his request and handed me a note, copy
                                    attached,<note n="39" xml:id="d80fn2">Not printed.</note>
                                setting forth the strong spirit of cooperation on the part of
                                Colombia in defense of this hemisphere. The Ambassador emphasized
                                the keen interest his Government felt in taking this course and its
                                earnest desire to continue to cooperate in every way contemplated by
                                the Habana and other preceding conferences.</p>
                            <p>I thanked him very profusely and emphasized our deep appreciation of
                                this fine spirit of alert cooperation.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>C[<hi rend="smallcaps">ordell</hi>] H[<hi rend="smallcaps">ull</hi>]</signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>